                    <p>The Covered Bridge, the largest source of income for the city, has New Metta well under hoof. In a
                        week, TCB Corporation pulls in enough cash to buy a small country. It's the ideal target, but security
                        is top-notch. Granu needs three things to survive this heist: a crew of specialists, impenetrable
                        sun protection, and gallons of grog.</p>

                    <p>There’s just one thing Granu doesn’t plan for—those damn meddling billy goats.</p>

